<lb />
からすが<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">頭</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あたま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">止</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">と</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>まった<lb />
